description: The image captures a presentation at a conference or seminar, bathed in blue and purple lighting. The main subject is a large screen displaying a slide titled "User Journey Automation," featuring a diagram with the concepts "Precision," "Rationale," and "Ambiguity" at the vertices of a shape enclosed in a circle. In the foreground, a man is crouched down working or adjusting equipment in front of the stage. The room appears to be a conference hall or ballroom, with decorative panels along the walls, and a patterned carpet. A partially visible audience member sits in the lower left corner.
